puzzle_name: Jigsaw Puzzle 1960 Mickey Moments - 1000 Pieces Puzzle
description: The Disney Collector's Edition is a lovingly designed collector's edition that brings together all the famous Disney classics: Aladdin, The Little Mermaid, Cinderella, The Jungle Book, The Lion King, Lady and the Tramp, and many, many more. Each puzzle is like a little trip into the wonderful fairy-tale world of Disney, which has lost none of its magic to this day. Their great stories of love, friendship, and heroism are absolutely timeless and bring back fond memories. Ravensburger puzzles mean premium-quality puzzle fun. They are backed by decades of experience in puzzle production and high standards of quality in terms of materials, motifs, and design. For example, the characteristic puzzle pieces are manufactured using punching tools that are still made today with extreme precision in Ravensburg, Upper Swabia. This passion for quality, attention to detail and a huge selection of motifs make Ravensburger puzzles so unique and guarantee an unforgettable puzzle experience. From beginners to professionals: every puzzle lover will find the perfect puzzle here!
